            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mt-1 font-medium">ШӘШӯЩ„ЩҠЩ„ Щ…ЩҒШөЩ    <div class="mb-6 print:hidden">
        <form method="get" class="space-y-4" data-live-search="true" data-live-search-delay="400">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-end gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
